Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my blood will burn on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:01:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ah fight on！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.38,0:00:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我还是个孩子 在一个疯狂的梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正仰望着那块约定之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们的梦的形状 喧嚣四起 心脏起跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 让我们共同前往那块土地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已无法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.11,0:01:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳跃吧 穿过白日阴沉 飞入光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想相信出生于这个世界是一件幸福的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.53,0:01:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开通往新时代的大门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,wow wow oh oh oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你是知道的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直都遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.81,0:01:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力斩断悲伤的根源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.48,0:01:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕 我们永远能在身边感受到彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.03,0:01:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 更多 更多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.69,0:01:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要将更多炙热的力量填满心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.12,0:01:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3, 4, 5
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒你的心跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.47,0:01:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让生命绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受心的脉动 燃烧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.92,0:01:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢而沸腾的心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现彼此的羁绊 高涨！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让生命绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受心的脉动 燃烧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加速到极限！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是来真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要更多谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.74,0:01:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装置已点火 心脏已起搏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰 火焰 火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的热血将燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.16,0:01:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 开战吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.25,0:22:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…And so, we met in the deep\Ndark and shattered place
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.81,0:22:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,no one will come to us. They\Nleft us here with disgrace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.00,0:22:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we're alone
