Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.88,0:03:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那颗不会跳动的心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战斗中根本帮不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有这个拳头就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？东
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...不见了？
