Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师说了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.82,0:03:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁...谁会说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说给你这种家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你听完可别绝望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:02.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石蕗老师认为你甚至连人类都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石蕗老师说了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.99,0:04:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是人类 而是石头
