Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石头 人类 石头 人类...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子怎么搞的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好诡异
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.49,0:04:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要敲碎她的脑袋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉安娜！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么鬼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是石头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:05:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再说这种莫名其妙的话了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这...这些全部是 这孩子的灵子？
